Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:32.72,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.64,Italics Top,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Wait a minute, Yuki! \NI don't think I'm ready for this yet!}Chờ đã Yuki! Em không nghĩ mình đã sẵn sàng cho nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.25,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai, why are you here?}S-Sao chị lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.68,Italics Top,Yuki,0,0,0,,{Then how do you want me to do it, Hayato?}Vậy em muốn anh làm thế nào, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:46.15,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{There's no way I'm making my sleepy \NKomari-chan go to school by herself.}Sao chị có thể để Komari-chan thiếu\N ngủ tự đi đến trường được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:45.60,Italics Top,Yuki,0,0,0,,{Just shove it in there? Like this?}Chỉ cần nhét nó vào đây. Như thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:47.50,Italics Top,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Á!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:51.89,Italics Top,Yuki,0,0,0,,{Oh, it might be too tight. \NI guess it's bigger than it looks.}A, có vẻ hơi khít. Hình như nó to hơn anh nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:54.76,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Not bad, huh? This is one that \NI save for very special occasions.}Không tệ nhỉ? Chị dành nó cho dịp đặc biệt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.76,Italics Top,Yuki,0,0,0,,{You have such a big ring finger, Hayato.}Hayato, ngón đeo nhẫn to ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:58.62,Italics Top,Hayato,0,0,0,,{I-I told you I'm a size 14!}E-Em đã nói là size 14 rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.66,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai...}C-Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.20,Italics Top,Yuki,0,0,0,,{Now, just hold still for me, okay?}Đừng di chuyển nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:00.99,Italics Top,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Don't put it in!}Đừng đút vào!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:04.09,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{T-Turn the volume down!}L-Làm ơn vặn nhỏ âm lượng...
